OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSewage: Ban water firm     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbonuses until discharges   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fend, Lib Dems say          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Liberal Democrats have urged the UK
OL,6, government to ban bonuses for water    
OL,7, company bosses until sewage offences   
OL,8, are stopped.                           
OL,10,FThe party's analysis showed firms in   
OL,11,FEngland had paid executives nearly #27m
OL,12,Fin bonuses since 2020.                 
OL,14,FThe bonuses are "obscene" given 1,000  
OL,15,Fsewage spills a day were recorded in   
OL,16,F2021, the Lib Dems said.               
OL,18,FThe government has not backed the ban, 
OL,19,Fbut said it was taking urgent action to
OL,20,Fcurb sewage discharges.                
